    "description": "<h3><a name=\"Description\"></a><b>Description</b></h3>\n\n<p>Execute the complete test suite for the DemoQA Elements module and validate results against defined Acceptance Criteria.</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3><a name=\"Activities\"></a><b>Activities</b></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Execute full test suite:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Run all automated and/or manual test scenarios</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Validate results:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Compare test outcomes against Acceptance Criteria (ACs)</li>\n\t\t<li>Ensure expected validation behavior is observed</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Review UI behavior and logs:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Verify UI states (error indicators, modal behavior, disabled interactions)</li>\n\t\t<li>Check execution logs for anomalies or errors</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Perform peer review:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Share results with QA/Team members</li>\n\t\t<li>Validate test coverage and result accuracy</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3><a name=\"ExpectedOutcome\"></a><b>Expected Outcome</b></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>All test cases executed successfully</li>\n\t<li>Results validated against Acceptance Criteria</li>\n\t<li>Any deviations or defects identified and documented</li>\n\t<li>Test results reviewed and approved by team</li>\n</ul>\n",
